reviewText: DVD Great  Learning and TEACHING DEVICE FOR YOUNGER PEOPLE COUPLING EDUCATION WITH A LOT OF FUN AND ENTERTAINMENT.
hello i am soo sorry even my husbind loves this it is awasome

The Kidsongs, is a great series of a bunch of Kids singing a lot of songs and doing some great moves! Each Kidsongs videotapes tells a different story.

In this story, the Kidsongs Kids and Billy and Ruby Biggle go to different places to sing and dance.

The songs in this cassette are:

"Walkin' The dog"

"Head, Shoulders, Knees and Toes"

"Alley Cat"

"La Bamba"

"Put Your Little Foot Right There"

"Loco-Motion"

"Peppermint Twist"

"Rock Around The Clock"

"Paw Paw Patch"

The songs are all really cute and fun to listen to. My baby-sitting charge, Garfield and I can't get enough of the Kidsongs cassettes! We both love it!

Lots Of Love,

  Fulliem XOXOXOXO
Boxed was damaged when received but tape is good.
Wish I could return it.  Did not hold attention of 2 or4 yr old children.  They love other kid song videos.
My 3 year old granddaughter loves this one! Have owned lots of kidsongs and this is a goodie!
Thank you for the replacement  of this birthday gift for a happy kid!
Great show for children, wish it would be on TV again.

Kidsongs are a great group of songs for young children. My granddaughter loved it between 2 to 6 years old so bought one for my 3 year old niece who I'm sure will love it as well. Even us adults loved it!
My son has autism and he is non verbal. He has been writing me notes about  this video and he was so thrilled when I got it for him for his birthday. Thanks
